cs.DC, cs.DB, cs.LG, cs.CR, cs.SE

The paper deals with the problem of predicting the performance of MapReduce applications, which is a topic related to distributed computing (cs.DC) and database systems (cs.DB). The paper also proposes a novel profile-guided progress indicator, which involves statistical curve fitting techniques, and thus falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the limitations of existing progress indicators and proposes a new approach to overcome them, which is related to cryptography and security (cs.CR) and software engineering (cs.SE).
